about.summary: Make fake data, supporting addresses, person names, dates, times, colors, coordinates, currencies, digital object identifiers ('DOIs'), jobs, phone numbers, 'DNA' sequences, doubles and integers from distributions and within a range.

Make fake data, supporting addresses, person names, dates, times, colors, coordinates, currencies, digital object identifiers ('DOIs'), jobs, phone numbers, 'DNA' sequences, doubles and integers from distributions and within a range.

name: r-charlatan
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.6.1" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-charlatan
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/charlatan_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/charlatan/charlatan_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: df862825330793339631b4aaeffa033c9d0d655e303127a478ca2de8c35679a7

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-r6 >=2.2.0
    - r-tibble >=1.2
    - r-whisker
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-r6 >=2.2.0
    - r-tibble >=1.2
    - r-whisker

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('charlatan')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('charlatan')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://docs.ropensci.org/charlatan/
  dev_url: https://github.com/ropensci/charlatan
  license: MIT
  summary: Make fake data, supporting addresses, person names, dates, times, colors, coordinates, currencies, digital object identifiers ('DOIs'), jobs, phone numbers, 'DNA' sequences, doubles and integers from distributions and within a range.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT'
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - thewchan
